text: Yahuud kee Nasaara nanu Yallih xaylooy kay kacnoytiiti itte, Nabiyow toysa sin dambittel macah sin digaalaa? wonna hinnay isin Yalli gineemik Seehada kinniton keenik ixxic, Yalli isih faxa marah dambi cabaah isih faxa mara digaalah, Yalli Qaranwaa kee baaxooy ken nammayih fanal taniimih Reeda-leeh Qhiyaamah ayró gacim kaâ fanah yakke
